text: Boca de Cupé is a corregimiento in Pinogana District, Darién Province, Panama with a population of 1,167 as of 2010. Its population as of 1990 was 901; its population as of 2000 was 902. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Darién Province Category:Road-inaccessible communities of Panama
title: Boca de Cupe
